# Scenario: Create a new pet
scenario: Create a new pet
  when I create a pet
    call ^createPet
      body: {"name": "Fluffy", "status": "available", "category": "cat", "price": 199.99}
  then the pet is created
    assert status 201
    assert $.name equals "Fluffy"
    assert $.status equals "available"
    extract $.id => newPetId
